# UI/UX Specifications and Design Requirements

## Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary**: #2563eb (Blue) - Main actions, links, highlights
- **Secondary**: #64748b (Slate) - Secondary actions, borders
- **Success**: #059669 (Green) - Success messages, positive actions
- **Warning**: #d97706 (Amber) - Warnings, alerts
- **Error**: #dc2626 (Red) - Error messages, destructive actions
- **Background**: #ffffff (White) - Main background
- **Surface**: #f8fafc (Light gray) - Card backgrounds, secondary surfaces
- **Text**: #1e293b (Dark slate) - Primary text
- **Text Secondary**: #64748b (Slate) - Secondary text, labels

### Typography
- **Font Family**: Inter (Primary), system fonts (Fallback)
- **Heading 1**: 2.25rem (36px), font-weight: 700
- **Heading 2**: 1.875rem (30px), font-weight: 600
- **Heading 3**: 1.5rem (24px), font-weight: 600
- **Body**: 1rem (16px), font-weight: 400
- **Small**: 0.875rem (14px), font-weight: 400
- **Caption**: 0.75rem (12px), font-weight: 400

### Spacing Scale
- **xs**: 0.25rem (4px)
- **sm**: 0.5rem (8px)
- **md**: 1rem (16px)
- **lg**: 1.5rem (24px)
- **xl**: 2rem (32px)
- **2xl**: 3rem (48px)

## Component Specifications

### Buttons
- **Primary Button**: Blue background, white text, rounded corners
- **Secondary Button**: White background, blue border and text
- **Danger Button**: Red background, white text
- **Button Sizes**: Small (32px), Medium (40px), Large (48px)
- **Hover States**: Slight opacity change, subtle shadow

### Forms
- **Input Fields**: 40px height, rounded borders, focus states
- **Labels**: Above inputs, required field indicators
- **Validation**: Real-time feedback, error messages below fields
- **Submit Buttons**: Full width, disabled state when invalid

### Cards
- **Background**: White with subtle shadow
- **Border Radius**: 8px
- **Padding**: 16px (24px for larger cards)
- **Hover Effects**: Subtle shadow increase

## Layout Structure

### Navigation
- **Header**: Fixed top, 64px height, logo + navigation + user menu
- **Sidebar**: Collapsible, 240px width when expanded
- **Main Content**: Responsive grid, max-width 1200px
- **Footer**: Minimal, links and copyright

### Responsive Breakpoints
- **Mobile**: < 768px (Single column, stacked navigation)
- **Tablet**: 768px - 1024px (Two column layout)
- **Desktop**: > 1024px (Full layout with sidebar)

### Grid System
- **Columns**: 12-column grid system
- **Gutters**: 16px between columns
- **Margins**: 16px on mobile, 24px on desktop

## Page-Specific Requirements

### Dashboard
- **Layout**: Grid of cards showing key metrics
- **Components**: Spending summary, recent expenses, quick actions
- **Charts**: Bar charts for spending by category, line charts for trends
- **Actions**: Quick expense entry, view all expenses

### Expense Entry Form
- **Layout**: Single column form with logical grouping
- **Progressive Disclosure**: Show advanced options on demand
- **Auto-save**: Save draft every 30 seconds
- **Validation**: Real-time feedback, clear error messages

### Expense List
- **Layout**: Table with sortable columns
- **Filters**: Date range, category, restaurant, amount
- **Search**: Global search across all fields
- **Pagination**: 20 items per page, infinite scroll option

### Restaurant Search
- **Layout**: Search bar + results grid
- **Search**: Autocomplete with recent searches
- **Results**: Card layout with key information
- **Actions**: Add to favorites, view details, select

## Accessibility Requirements

### WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance
- **Color Contrast**: Minimum 4.5:1 for normal text
- **Keyboard Navigation**: Full functionality without mouse
- **Screen Reader**: Proper ARIA labels and landmarks
- **Focus Management**: Visible focus indicators

### Mobile Accessibility
- **Touch Targets**: Minimum 44px Ã— 44px
- **Gesture Support**: Swipe, pinch, tap gestures
- **Orientation**: Support for portrait and landscape
- **Offline**: Basic functionality without internet

## Performance Requirements

### Loading States
- **Skeleton Screens**: Show content structure while loading
- **Progressive Loading**: Load critical content first
- **Lazy Loading**: Images and non-critical content
- **Caching**: Cache static assets and API responses

### Animation Guidelines
- **Duration**: 150ms for micro-interactions, 300ms for page transitions
- **Easing**: Smooth, natural motion curves
- **Reduced Motion**: Respect user preferences
- **Performance**: 60fps animations, no layout thrashing

## User Experience Patterns

### Error Handling
- **User-Friendly Messages**: Clear, actionable error text
- **Recovery Options**: Suggest solutions or alternatives
- **Graceful Degradation**: Functionality continues with reduced features
- **Logging**: Track errors for debugging

### Success Feedback
- **Confirmation Messages**: Clear success indicators
- **Progress Indicators**: Show completion status
- **Celebration**: Subtle animations for achievements
- **Next Steps**: Guide users to next actions

### Data Management
- **Auto-save**: Prevent data loss
- **Undo/Redo**: Allow users to correct mistakes
- **Bulk Actions**: Efficient management of multiple items
- **Export Options**: Data portability in multiple formats
